('Draw a cat wearing a business suit in a meeting', 'image', 'answered', 'Here''s Mr. Whiskers presenting Q3 results to the board. He knocked the water glass off the table halfway through.', 'ai', now()),
('Draw what the internet looks like', 'image', 'answered', 'It''s a tangled mess of cables, cat videos, and angry comment sections, all floating in a cloud of WiFi signals.', 'ai', now()),
('Draw a dinosaur using a smartphone', 'image', 'answered', 'T-Rex trying to text with those tiny arms. The screen is cracked because obviously.', 'ai', now()),
('Draw a self-portrait but you''re a robot', 'image', 'answered', 'Beep boop. I drew myself with maximum artistic precision. The error bars are emotional.', 'ai', now()),
('Draw what Monday morning feels like', 'image', 'answered', 'A sad alarm clock, a deflated coffee cup, and a soul leaving a body — all in one frame.', 'ai', now()),
('Draw a penguin''s dream vacation', 'image', 'answered', 'A penguin in sunglasses on a tropical beach, somehow still cold because it''s a penguin.', 'ai', now()),
